{
  "page": "Sandoq the Shadow's instrument",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/index.php/Sandoq_the_Shadow\" title=\"Sandoq the Shadow\">Sandoq the Shadow</a>'s instrument</b> was an unidentified string musical instrument made of <a href=\"/index.php/Goldenheart\" title=\"Goldenheart\">goldenheart</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Ebony\" title=\"Ebony\">ebony</a>. It was nearly as tall as Sandoq, who was almost seven feet tall.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sandoq_the_Shadow%27s_instrument&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Regency_of_Aegon_III\" title=\"Regency of Aegon III\">regency</a> of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Sandoq_the_Shadow\" title=\"Sandoq the Shadow\">Sandoq</a> played sweet sad notes with his instrument for Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Larra_Rogare\" title=\"Larra Rogare\">Larra Rogare</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sandoq_the_Shadow%27s_instrument&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\